      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison — nominal completion",
      "description": "Particle image velocimetry (PIV) measurements at five impeller speeds (1500, 2000, 2500, 3000, 3500 RPM) were compared against CFD-predicted velocity fields. All five simulation runs completed nominally with residuals converging below 1e-5. RMS velocity error was within 8% across all operating points. No solver exceptions, NaN fields, or divergence events were encountered during the comparison campaign.",
      "outcome": "pass",
      "quantitativeResult": "Mean RMS velocity error 6.3%; maximum 7.9% at 3500 RPM"
