      "description": "Predicted relative hemolysis index (RHI) values from the CFD-Python post-processing pipeline were compared against bench haemolysis measurements across the five flow-speed combinations defined in the COU. All pipeline executions completed without runtime errors or numerical warnings. RHI predictions satisfied the RH < 1 acceptance criterion at all operating points.",
      "outcome": "pass",
      "quantitativeResult": "RHI range 0.61–0.94 (all < 1.0 acceptance threshold)"
