      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "GCI for volume-averaged scalar shear stress below 5% on the fine mesh.",
      "rationale": "Mesh sensitivity study across three refinement levels yielded GCI of 1.8% on the fine mesh (11.2M cells), well within the 5% criterion. Second-order spatial discretisation was employed throughout. Discretization error is considered adequately characterised for the nominal operating envelope."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
